      "line": 15,
      "message": "Ok i just realized why are we having test failing due to linting issues in _molecule_internal_role_, not oom tested role - it's because of this inclusion. So far we did nowhere came upon issues with linting prepare-docker role because natively it's out of scope of tested roles, and once you included it here it is... And that is the reason for https://jira.onap.org/browse/OOM-1850 And another reason for what i wrote above - molecule roles should not be put into test scope.",
      "author": {
