      "file_path": "ansible/test/play-infrastructure/molecule/default/molecule.yml",
      "patchset_number": 8,
      "line": 18,
      "message": "It's working correctly outside of the scope of this commit because in docker/molecule/default/molecule.yml there is no mount bind for /var/run/docker.sock, it's only here in your commit so effectively you're trying to use unsupported 'mode' here (running 'docker' role in a container with mount binded /var/run/docker.sock).",
